My program is using the the both classes 'VerilatedVcdC'(for GTKWave interactive mode) and 'VerilatedFstC'(for file dump).<br>
Exclusive selection without re-compilation.<br>
It seems to need a common base class/interface definition for those.<br>
as like below.<br>

```
interface VerilatedC {
     virtual void open(const char* filename) VL_MT_UNSAFE_ONE = 0;
     virtual void close() VL_MT_UNSAFE_ONE = 0;
     ...
};

class VerilatedVcdC public VerilatedC {
...
}
class VerilatedFstC public VerilatedC {
...
}

VerilatedC    pDump = new VerilatedVcdC (...);

```

Is it possible?

